WEBVTT

00:01:28.497 --> 00:01:32.456
ljudski mozak.

00:01:32.456 --> 00:01:34.839
Djetlići inače

00:01:34.839 --> 00:01:37.027
kljucaju, udaraju glavom

00:01:37.027 --> 00:01:42.318
o drvo po tisuće puta
dnevno svaki dan. Svaki dan!

00:01:42.318 --> 00:01:44.231
I koliko svi mi znamo,

00:01:44.231 --> 00:01:45.437
to im nimalo ne smeta.

00:01:45.437 --> 00:01:47.703
Kako to?

00:01:47.703 --> 00:01:50.629
Njihov se mozak ne mućka poput našega,

00:01:50.629 --> 00:01:53.341
već je čvrsto naguran,

00:01:53.341 --> 00:01:56.197
barem za udarce sprijeda.

00:01:56.197 --> 00:01:58.140
Nije se puno ljudi bavilo

00:01:58.140 --> 00:02:01.224
tim istraživanjem
sve do zadnjih nekoliko godina